text:
Cairnhill Community Club CCMC Project 30-30 core team Charmaine Eolhc and I visited The Giving Garden at Kim Tian West this morning, lots to learn.

They have resident volunteers & Community in Bloom Ambassador, Farm Gaya Felicia Tan will be there to give guidance and answer any questions related to edible plants on Every Sunday, 9am - 12 noon

Beautiful place
Nice people
Great atmosphere.
